----------------------------
Requirements
----------------------------

- Java 7
- ant-doxygen >= 1.6.1
- apache-log4j = 1.2.17

----------------------------
Install Dependencies
----------------------------

- Obtain ant-doxygen from 
  http://sourceforge.net/projects/ant-doxygen 
  and extract to lib_local/ant-doxygen
- Obtain apache-log4j from 
  http://logging.apache.org/log4j/1.2/download.html 
  and extract to lib_local/apache-log4j-1.2.17

----------------------------
Building
----------------------------

1. Install dependencies.

2. Just use the provided ant script 
   build.xml and call "ant build_and_package".


----------------------------
Usage
----------------------------

For GUI version:
  java -jar riscVivid.jar [-g]
For non interactive version:
  java -jar riscVivid.jar -c config_file.cfg
For help message:
  java -jar riscVivid.jar -h
About & license information:
  java -jar riscVivid.jar -about

